CatDescriptText: Headline for related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, pg. 17, reads: "Jones Inducted as Councilman"
TitMainTitle: Five Pittsburgh City Council members, from left: Patrick T. Fagan, Paul F. Jones, Bennett Rodgers, Emmanuel F. Schifano, and Fredrick G. Weir, taking seats behind wooden desks with flowers in foreground in Pittsburgh City Council Chambers, City County Building
